00:50:25.863 --> 00:50:29.565
'Oh, wow, I want to talk to my angel.

00:50:29.565 --> 00:50:35.575
' Oh, do not do this!

00:50:40.120 --> 00:50:40.337
I look to the Father.

00:50:40.337 --> 00:50:43.200
He is the author and the finisher of my faith.

00:50:43.200 --> 00:50:45.200
He is everything to me.

00:51:01.434 --> 00:51:01.737
An angel is really cool to look at for a minute, but he is beautiful beyond description.

00:51:01.737 --> 00:51:07.469
He is too marvelous for words, too wonderful for comprehension, like nothing ever seen or heard.

00:51:07.469 --> 00:51:10.180
Who can grasp his infinite wisdom?

00:51:10.180 --> 00:51:14.507
Who can fathom the depth of his love?

00:51:14.507 --> 00:51:16.425
He is beautiful beyond description, majesty enthroned above.

00:51:16.425 --> 00:51:20.720
That's why I believe that song came out: 'I stand, I stand in awe of you.

00:51:20.720 --> 00:51:24.920
' Even the angels are in awe of him—the ones that are on his side.

00:51:24.920 --> 00:51:33.480
The devil has come to kill, steal, and destroy and to confuse you, to bring haze over your relationship, to bring fog.

00:51:33.480 --> 00:51:37.525
Whatever they could do—marine spirits, and people get all into that.

00:51:37.525 --> 00:51:44.560
I'm going to tell you this: I do not get into talking to them even when you're casting them out of somebody.

00:51:47.644 --> 00:51:47.880
I don't ask, 'How many are in there?

00:51:47.880 --> 00:51:48.504
What's your origin?

00:51:48.504 --> 00:51:51.000
How long have you been in here?

00:51:51.000 --> 00:51:52.950
What's your name?

00:51:52.950 --> 00:51:54.510
' Who cares?

00:52:02.820 --> 00:52:03.440
Get out!

00:52:03.440 --> 00:52:07.320
I'm not here to be your friend.

00:52:12.860 --> 00:52:13.080
I don't care about you; you're a liar.

00:52:33.047 --> 00:52:33.533
They don't tell the truth anyway.

00:52:33.533 --> 00:52:36.440
So, 'How are you?

00:52:36.440 --> 00:52:43.274
Well, devil, what's your name and what's your origin?

00:52:53.520 --> 00:52:53.689
And how many of you are in there?

00:52:53.689 --> 00:53:02.093
' Whoever you are and however many of you there are, get out in the name of Jesus!

00:53:02.093 --> 00:53:11.791
I do not listen to you because there's nothing they say that is the truth.

00:53:11.791 --> 00:53:15.238
They're liars.

00:53:15.238 --> 00:53:19.390
He is the father of lies.

00:53:19.390 --> 00:53:21.778
Why would you ask a liar how many there are?

00:53:21.778 --> 00:53:22.400
'There's 20.

00:53:22.400 --> 00:53:30.029
' I mean, do you think they're going to tell you the truth?

00:53:30.029 --> 00:53:33.315
'Well, I command you to tell me how many in there.

00:53:33.315 --> 00:53:34.730
' 'There's 15 of me.

00:53:34.730 --> 00:53:37.320
' Seriously, why are you communicating with them?

00:53:41.238 --> 00:53:42.433
You all play around with fire.

00:53:42.433 --> 00:53:45.063
There's a lot of dumb Christians.

00:53:45.063 --> 00:53:46.640
Jesus did it in one instance.

00:53:46.640 --> 00:53:48.880
He didn't go around talking to the devil.

00:53:48.880 --> 00:53:49.245
'How many of them?

00:53:49.245 --> 00:53:58.065
' Well, he said, 'They are legion, for we are many.

00:53:58.065 --> 00:54:05.830
' He did it one time.

00:54:05.840 --> 00:54:10.929
But I don't go around making it a habit talking to devils.

00:54:10.929 --> 00:54:16.869
One time with the madman of Gadara, he went around talking to him and said, 'Get out.

00:54:16.869 --> 00:54:18.090
Go to the pigs.

00:54:18.090 --> 00:54:21.475
' I'm telling y'all, don't be talking to devils.

00:54:21.475 --> 00:54:23.400
Don't be talking to stuff.

00:54:23.400 --> 00:54:27.280
Talk to the Holy Ghost.

00:54:43.080 --> 00:54:43.507
You need to take more time praying in the spirit instead of talking to devils.

00:54:43.507 --> 00:54:51.730
Well, I hear people say, 'Well, I have deliverance services and I do this all the time.

00:54:51.730 --> 00:55:00.155
' Okay, if you feel like that's your calling and you want to help people out, great.

00:55:11.045 --> 00:55:11.260
But don't be talking to demons and hanging out.

00:55:11.260 --> 00:55:15.862
I don't get my kicks and giggles off of that stuff.

00:55:15.862 --> 00:55:24.400
I want to see people delivered, saved, and healed and baptized in the Holy Ghost.

00:55:24.400 --> 00:55:26.620
That's what my mission is.

00:55:27.640 --> 00:55:29.280
So maybe that's your thing, but that's not us.

00:55:29.280 --> 00:55:31.040
I just get tired of it.

00:55:47.891 --> 00:55:48.103
I was bound by eight of them.

00:56:01.040 --> 00:56:22.462
And whenever you have the torment that I walked through for so many years—and was tormented and almost went to the nut house—my mom and dad almost put me in an insane asylum because of how bad I was.

00:56:22.462 --> 00:56:30.120
But finally, God set me free.

00:56:30.120 --> 00:56:36.787
I tried to physically hurt my mom all the time.

00:56:36.787 --> 00:56:39.080
It was bad.

00:56:39.080 --> 00:56:43.712
People don't understand what it's truly like to be bound.

00:56:43.712 --> 00:56:47.502
A lot of you don't know.

00:56:47.502 --> 00:56:57.560
When you are, they want to put you so sedated with medical attention and all the things that I had to go through.

00:56:57.560 --> 00:57:00.560
And Jesus set me free.

00:57:04.142 --> 00:57:05.338
I know what it's like to truly be bound for a long time.

00:57:05.338 --> 00:57:06.537
And Jesus set me free.

00:57:20.476 --> 00:57:20.764
I don't talk about it; I don't give them glory.

00:57:26.040 --> 00:57:49.120
But I'm going to tell you, I've seen the darkest side where you're ready to kill yourself and you don't feel like there's any hope and you're at the bottom of the barrel and the barrel's on top of you, thinking, 'God, is there a God out there that cares?

00:57:49.120 --> 00:57:57.280
' when you're so depressed and having so much demonic influence going on.

00:57:57.280 --> 00:58:14.027
You've got stuff moving around in your room, radios turning on, and demonic TV shows coming on in the middle of the night.

00:58:14.027 --> 00:58:17.463
I've been there.

00:58:17.463 --> 00:58:24.891
And for whom the Son has set free is free indeed.

00:58:24.891 --> 00:58:27.870
But I don't play around with the devil.

00:58:34.600 --> 00:58:35.210
He comes to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:58:47.383 --> 00:58:47.634
And a lot of you, like I said, you get kicks and giggles off of it.

00:58:50.686 --> 00:58:51.131
I don't.

00:58:51.131 --> 00:58:53.639
It makes me furious.

00:58:53.639 --> 00:58:56.736
It was way too real to me.

00:58:56.736 --> 00:59:00.790
But Jesus set me free.

00:59:00.790 --> 00:59:07.775
Jesus paid the price for me to be free.

00:59:08.265 --> 00:59:11.000
And I'm so thankful for this communion.

00:59:14.183 --> 00:59:19.480
I take it more now than I ever have after Jesus set me free.

00:59:30.520 --> 00:59:31.000
I don't keep my vessel empty.

00:59:31.000 --> 00:59:36.600
They always try to come back with their buddies—eight more of them.

00:59:36.600 --> 00:59:42.345
They come to see if it's empty.

00:59:51.330 --> 00:59:51.500
I keep myself full.

00:59:51.500 --> 00:59:53.960
I'll never be tormented another day in my life.

00:59:53.960 --> 01:00:02.440
Out of experience, a lot of you have no idea that if you open the door for the devil, he'll take a mile.

01:00:02.440 --> 01:00:09.580
He'll destroy you and he'll take you to the bottom of the pit with him.

01:00:18.600 --> 01:00:18.983
And I'm telling you, you say, 'Well, I worship the devil.

01:00:18.983 --> 01:00:21.280
' You're an idiot.

01:00:26.400 --> 01:00:28.470
There will be a day when the devils you think you control will drag your soul to hell.

01:00:28.470 --> 01:00:30.789
Ask Anton LaVey.

01:00:30.789 --> 01:00:33.450
He said, 'Oh no, what have I done?

01:00:33.450 --> 01:00:35.813
Oh no, what have I done?

01:00:35.813 --> 01:00:39.800
' the moment he was taking his last breath.

01:00:39.800 --> 01:00:40.700
Isn't that amazing?

01:00:45.823 --> 01:00:49.338
The very devils you thought you controlled and you sacrificed to for your power—'Oh no, what have I done?

01:00:49.338 --> 01:00:52.120
' They were dragging him to hell.

01:00:54.531 --> 01:00:54.754
And there's nothing you can do about it.

01:00:58.520 --> 01:00:58.777
You can't cry out to Jesus then.

01:00:58.777 --> 01:01:10.080
What are you doing when you're taking your last breath and they've grabbed a hold of you and they're dragging you to that pit of fire to torment forever and ever and ever?

01:01:20.040 --> 01:01:20.240
And there's many of you that say you practice the occult and you watch me.

01:01:31.990 --> 01:01:32.480
You know, we find you fascinating.

01:01:35.167 --> 01:01:35.895
You say we practice Satanism and we watch you.

01:01:35.895 --> 01:01:44.440
Well, we practice soothsaying and we want to know how you see because we want to see what you see.

01:01:44.440 --> 01:01:46.136
We're into New Age and astrology.

01:01:46.136 --> 01:01:51.250
I have all kinds of people tell me that.

01:01:54.560 --> 01:01:56.453
They say, "You know, we watch you, Brandon.

01:01:56.453 --> 01:02:00.840
" I have a lot of the occult; they tell us, they email us.

01:02:00.840 --> 01:02:05.393
But you don't understand there's a day of reckoning coming for you.

01:02:05.393 --> 01:02:19.408
There will be a day when the very demons you think you can control will drag your soul to hell.

01:02:19.744 --> 01:02:24.560
It will happen if you don't repent and turn to the Lord.

01:02:24.560 --> 01:02:28.360
Well, I sold my soul to the devil.

01:02:28.360 --> 01:02:29.491
It's a lie.

01:02:29.491 --> 01:02:31.580
Your soul doesn't belong to the devil.

01:02:31.580 --> 01:02:33.729
Your soul belongs to Jesus Christ.

01:02:49.160 --> 01:02:58.267
And the moment you confess Jesus Christ as your Lord and Savior, the moment He forgives you of all your sins, there's no one in a darker place that they can't get out of.

01:02:58.267 --> 01:02:59.996
I don't care what you've done.

01:02:59.996 --> 01:03:01.240
Well, I've sacrificed cats.

01:03:01.240 --> 01:03:03.512
I had this one girl.

01:03:03.512 --> 01:03:09.671
She had pentagrams and she had carved them all in her hands.

01:03:09.671 --> 01:03:16.107
And as we were casting the devils out of her, those pentagrams flared up and were huge.

01:03:16.520 --> 01:03:19.400
And because she had blood flowing, her eyes went like a cat's.

01:03:19.400 --> 01:03:27.740
She had sacrificed things on an altar—black cats and killed cats and doing everything for satanic power.

01:03:27.740 --> 01:03:34.120
She was at the church and nobody at the church could get her free.

01:03:34.453 --> 01:03:38.289
And so they had to come and get the janitor.

01:03:38.289 --> 01:03:46.333
They said, "We don't know what to do with this, but we know you deal with stuff like this.

01:03:46.333 --> 01:03:48.017
So could you help us?

01:03:52.543 --> 01:03:53.337
" I said, "I'm the janitor.

01:03:53.337 --> 01:03:56.040
You're a pastor.

01:03:56.040 --> 01:03:59.989
You told me not to pray for anybody.

01:03:59.989 --> 01:04:03.145
" I was not trying to be sarcastic.

01:04:18.265 --> 01:04:18.740
It was just the truth.

01:04:18.740 --> 01:04:31.547
But as we went back there, I'll never forget as she was begging for help and those demons were clawing her throat and they were coming out of her.

01:04:38.540 --> 01:04:41.039
And yet you play with something that you think is your friend and they give you power for a season as you watch these videos.

01:04:43.760 --> 01:04:47.560
And I try to tell you, Jesus is the only way.

01:04:47.560 --> 01:04:51.440
He wants to save your soul.

01:04:54.160 --> 01:05:00.503
And the Lord told us, He said, "I want to save all of the occultists.

01:05:00.503 --> 01:05:02.017
I want to bring them out of that.

01:05:02.017 --> 01:05:04.840
" Brandon, I don't want anybody to go to hell.

01:05:04.840 --> 01:05:11.030
Unless a man is born again, he cannot enter into the kingdom of God.

01:05:11.030 --> 01:05:16.380
But He said, "Brandon, I want them all to get born again.

01:05:31.133 --> 01:05:32.947
I love them all.

01:05:32.947 --> 01:05:34.600
" They're deceived by the devil.

01:05:34.600 --> 01:05:38.860
Satan has blinded the eyes of the unbeliever, Brandon.

01:05:38.860 --> 01:05:43.720
But I wish that none should perish, but all come to repentance.

01:05:45.987 --> 01:05:47.427
And I think that's very interesting.

01:05:47.427 --> 01:05:50.743
You're in flat rebellion towards Him, but He says, "I love you.

01:06:01.748 --> 01:06:01.976
I love them.

01:06:02.888 --> 01:06:06.147
I love those that are so far off, Brandon.

01:06:09.444 --> 01:06:10.904
They sacrificed to the devil and they worship him, but I love them.

01:06:17.196 --> 01:06:17.942
" There's no greater love than this: than a man who lays down his life for his brother.

01:06:17.942 --> 01:06:30.260
Jesus laid His life down for every one of us and He paid the price for every one of us to be born again.

01:06:30.260 --> 01:06:35.520
People are asking me, Braden, "Can I do self-deliverance on myself?

01:06:35.520 --> 01:06:42.110
" Yeah, you can do self-deliverance on yourself, but it's not ideal.

01:06:53.185 --> 01:06:53.430
It's better when you have a group fast and pray and seek Him.

01:06:53.920 --> 01:06:56.885
But if you live a fasted lifestyle, you don't have to say, "Time out.

01:06:56.885 --> 01:07:05.298
We've got to go fast because we've got to get the devil out of somebody," to deal with this unbelief.

01:07:05.298 --> 01:07:10.863
Because they'll flip out and growl and act all kinds of crazy stuff.

01:07:24.387 --> 01:07:24.814
What are you going to do then?

01:07:24.814 --> 01:07:36.017
Because your flesh gets in, and the moment you lay hands on them in fear, they get strength from you.

01:07:36.017 --> 01:07:43.533
Many of you don't know that because you have more fear in the ability of that devil freaking out right then.

01:07:59.143 --> 01:07:59.651
And the moment you lay hands on them, they draw that fear out of you because fear is faith contaminated.

01:07:59.651 --> 01:08:01.120
They draw power from fear.

01:08:01.120 --> 01:08:02.326
They are fear.

01:08:02.326 --> 01:08:08.491
But most Christians just play around with stuff.

01:08:08.491 --> 01:08:14.200
But I just want to tell you all, Jesus loves you.

01:08:22.956 --> 01:08:23.098
And I bring this to you tonight.

01:08:23.098 --> 01:08:23.800
Is everything okay?

01:08:23.800 --> 01:08:24.173
Yeah.

01:08:24.173 --> 01:08:27.288
They're asking, "Did she get free?

01:08:27.288 --> 01:08:29.249
" They're saying, "Yeah, she got free.

01:08:29.249 --> 01:08:29.640
" Who?

01:08:30.680 --> 01:08:30.939
The girl.

01:08:30.939 --> 01:08:31.719
Oh, yeah.

01:08:31.719 --> 01:08:32.908
She got free.

01:08:44.806 --> 01:08:45.143
Of course she did.

01:08:45.143 --> 01:08:48.715
Yes.

01:08:48.715 --> 01:08:54.062
Sorry, I went squirrel.

01:08:54.062 --> 01:08:55.680
"Did she get free, Brandon?

01:08:55.680 --> 01:08:58.910
" Yes.

01:08:58.920 --> 01:08:59.594
Yes.

01:08:59.594 --> 01:09:00.606
I'm sorry.

01:09:00.606 --> 01:09:02.020
She came to church.

01:09:02.020 --> 01:09:04.020
She came and got plugged in at church.

01:09:04.020 --> 01:09:05.160
She got free.

01:09:05.160 --> 01:09:05.800
Yes.

01:09:05.800 --> 01:09:08.560
"You've got to finish the story!

01:09:14.617 --> 01:09:14.909
What is wrong with you?

01:09:14.909 --> 01:09:19.224
We're on the edge of our seat here.

01:09:19.224 --> 01:09:21.216
Did she get free?

01:09:21.216 --> 01:09:21.880
" Yes.

01:09:26.319 --> 01:09:26.734
And her daddy, too.

01:09:26.734 --> 01:09:28.395
Her daddy, too.

01:09:28.395 --> 01:09:29.640
They came.

01:09:29.640 --> 01:09:54.328
They drove a black Dodge truck.

01:09:54.328 --> 01:10:24.990
I'll never forget it.

01:10:25.000 --> 01:10:34.950
They came to the back.

01:10:34.960 --> 01:10:59.430
She had short black hair and she started coming.

01:10:59.440 --> 01:11:12.547
She came to church and then they left.

01:11:12.547 --> 01:11:32.670
I don't know where they went, but they left after a while.

01:11:32.680 --> 01:11:51.727
But her and her dad both got born again.

01:11:51.727 --> 01:12:24.590
And he had a big old beard; he was a gnarly man.

01:12:24.600 --> 01:12:27.029
Oh, we just love on people.

01:12:27.029 --> 01:12:28.862
Don't you know Jesus loves you?

01:12:28.862 --> 01:12:32.080
He loves you so much.

01:12:33.783 --> 01:12:41.867
The power of the Holy Ghost dwells on the inside of you.

01:12:41.867 --> 01:13:05.582
And even when that angel came and told me, he said, "There's a new mantle coming on you today.

01:13:05.582 --> 01:13:16.733
Things are changing for you quickly.

01:13:16.733 --> 01:13:19.440
" There was a lot more.

01:13:19.440 --> 01:13:46.770
He said, and then he looked to the Father.

01:13:46.770 --> 01:14:02.858
But I think it's interesting, y'all.

01:14:04.013 --> 01:14:04.302
I do.

01:14:06.480 --> 01:14:17.710
I love the spirit realm, but Satan is a loser.

01:14:17.720 --> 01:14:38.485
That's what I tried to tell y'all.

01:14:38.485 --> 01:14:39.943
He lost.

01:14:39.943 --> 01:15:01.416
The Bible says that Jesus triumphed over him and He made a display of him openly.

01:15:01.416 --> 01:15:03.853
He triumphed over him.

01:15:03.853 --> 01:15:37.160
He paraded him around to everyone and they made a display of him openly, showing that He was the victor and he was the loser.

01:15:37.160 --> 01:15:58.550
Jesus is a winner.

01:15:58.560 --> 01:16:03.176
He defeated him fair and square.

01:16:03.176 --> 01:16:06.439
Do you understand?

01:16:06.439 --> 01:16:10.480
There was no cheating.

01:16:10.480 --> 01:16:18.070
God didn't cheat.

01:16:18.080 --> 01:16:24.535
God whipped him once and for all.

01:16:24.535 --> 01:17:08.163
He paid the price for you and me to walk in victory.

01:17:08.163 --> 01:17:23.440
Why do we allow the devil to torment us?

01:17:23.440 --> 01:17:29.308
Why do we give him any place?

01:17:46.611 --> 01:17:47.366
The Bible says, "Give no place to the devil.

01:17:47.366 --> 01:17:50.676
" But many of you are buddies with him.

01:17:50.676 --> 01:18:01.575
Give no place to the devil.

01:18:01.575 --> 01:18:06.380
Don't be his buddy.

01:18:06.380 --> 01:18:13.715
Kick him out of your house.

01:18:13.715 --> 01:18:26.747
I try not to be too funny about it, but it's that serious.

01:18:26.747 --> 01:18:33.184
Don't accept a poo-poo package.

01:18:33.184 --> 01:18:38.430
Don't be friends with the devil.

01:18:38.440 --> 01:18:42.773
Give no place to the devil.

01:18:42.773 --> 01:18:53.750
Like I said, most of you don't understand what you're doing and you just ignorantly do it.

01:18:53.750 --> 01:19:04.830
But then some of you are doing it with your eyes wide open.

01:19:04.840 --> 01:19:21.371
That's why I take communion all the time.

01:19:21.371 --> 01:19:25.480
I give no place to the devil.

01:19:25.480 --> 01:19:33.507
I make sure any door I may open, I keep them shut.

01:19:33.507 --> 01:19:53.847
I have been bound, but I am free.

01:19:53.847 --> 01:20:06.753
And I will never go back there.

01:20:06.753 --> 01:20:12.390
Never.

01:20:16.160 --> 01:20:17.880
For whom the Son has set free is free indeed.

01:20:17.880 --> 01:20:46.480
He that is begotten of God keepeth himself, and the wicked one toucheth him not.

01:21:40.200 --> 01:21:43.494
The wicked one toucheth you not.

01:22:01.560 --> 01:22:01.920
A curse without a cause cannot stand.

01:22:01.920 --> 01:22:04.605
Father, I thank You, Lord, for the blood.

01:22:04.605 --> 01:22:07.455
I thank You for Your body.

01:22:07.455 --> 01:22:12.834
I thank You, Father, for this time we just talk about things.

01:22:29.844 --> 01:22:30.408
You know, when I told you the devil visited me, he couldn't do anything.

01:22:31.160 --> 01:22:31.627
You know why?

01:22:31.627 --> 01:22:35.320
Because the blood of Jesus was against him.

01:22:35.320 --> 01:22:36.434
This communion.

01:22:36.434 --> 01:22:41.736
Do you understand the power of the name of Jesus?

01:22:41.736 --> 01:22:52.394
At the name of Jesus, every knee will bow and every tongue will confess that He is Lord.

01:22:58.520 --> 01:23:05.840
And I try to tell you all, he offered me everything that your flesh would ever want—money, fame, cars.

